microTasks.description:
Create another helper function called addCaddyConfig that takes subdomain and port as parameters. The function should: 1) Define caddyConfigPath as '/etc/caddy/Caddyfile', 2) Create config block string: `
${subdomain}.gen3.ai {
  reverse_proxy localhost:${port}
}
`, 3) Append to Caddyfile using fs.appendFileSync(caddyConfigPath, configBlock), 4) Reload Caddy with execSync('systemctl reload caddy'). Wrap in try-catch and log any errors.
